Affiliation = {Zimmer, L (Corresponding Author), Univ Freiburg, Inst Comp Sci, D-79085 Freiburg, Germany.
   Zimmer, Lucas, Univ Freiburg, Inst Comp Sci, D-79085 Freiburg, Germany.
