Affiliation = {Eldeeb, H (Corresponding Author), Univ Tartu, Inst Comp Sci, Data Syst Grp, EE-51009 Tartu, Estonia.
   Eldeeb, Hassan; Maher, Mohamed; Elshawi, Radwa; Sakr, Sherif, Univ Tartu, Inst Comp Sci, EE-51009 Tartu, Estonia.
