Affiliation = {Qiao, YN (Corresponding Author), Xi An Jiao Tong Univ, Sch Comp Sci \& Technol, 28 Xianning West Rd, Xian 710049, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
   Yang, Fan; Qiao, Yanan; Wang, Shan; Wang, Xiao, Xi An Jiao Tong Univ, Sch Comp Sci \& Technol, 28 Xianning West Rd, Xian 710049, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
