   Soulen, Michael C.; Stavropoulos, S. William, Hosp Univ Penn, Dept Radiol, Div Intervent Radiol, 3400 Spruce St, Philadelphia, PA 19104 USA.
   McGirr, Aidan; Singh, Sukhdeep; Silva, Alvin, Mayo Clin, Dept Radiol, Phoenix, AZ USA.
   Chang, Ken, Massachusetts Gen Hosp, Dept Radiol, Athinoula A Martinos Ctr Biomed Imaging, Boston, MA USA.
   Huang, Raymond Y., Brigham \& Womens Hosp, Dept Radiol, 75 Francis St, Boston, MA 02115 USA.
   Zhang, Paul J., Hosp Univ Penn, Dept Pathol, Philadelphia, PA 19104 USA.
   Hu, Rong, Cent South Univ, Sch Comp Sci \& Engn, Changsha, Hunan, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1038/s41598-020-76132-z},
