Affiliation = {Kulbach, C (Corresponding Author), Res Ctr Informat Technol FZI, Haid \& Neu Str 10-14, D-76131 Karlsruhe, Germany.
   Kulbach, Cedric; Heyden, Marco, Res Ctr Informat Technol FZI, Haid \& Neu Str 10-14, D-76131 Karlsruhe, Germany.
