Affiliation = {Humm, BG (Corresponding Author), Darmstadt Univ Appl Sci, Dept Comp Sci, Schofferstr 3, D-64295 Darmstadt, Germany.
   Brand, Lisa; Krajewski, Andrea, Darmstadt Univ Appl Sci, Dept Media, Schofferstr 3, D-64295 Darmstadt, Germany.
