Affiliation = {Liu, YA (Corresponding Author), Virginia Polytech Inst \& State Univ, Dept Chem Engn, AspenTech Ctr Excellence Proc Syst Engn, Blacksburg, VA 24061 USA.
   Agarwal, Aman; Liu, Y. A., Virginia Polytech Inst \& State Univ, Dept Chem Engn, AspenTech Ctr Excellence Proc Syst Engn, Blacksburg, VA 24061 USA.
