   Haq, Ejaz Ul; Inseeyong, Nantawoot; Laonamsai, Jeerapong; Chuenchum, Pavisorn, Chulalongkorn Univ, Fac Engn, Dept Water Resources Engn, Bangkok 10300, Thailand.
   Laonamsai, Jeerapong; Chuenchum, Pavisorn, Chulalongkorn Univ, Ctr Excellence Disaster \& Risk Management Informat, Bangkok 10300, Thailand.
   Pakoksung, Kwanchai, Burapha Univ, Fac Engn, Dept Civil Engn, Chon Buri 20131, Thailand.
   Xu, Mengzhen, Tsinghua Univ, State Key Lab Hydrosci \& Engn, Beijing 100084, Peoples R China.
