Affiliation = {Sánchez-DelaCruz, E (Corresponding Author), Tecnol Nacl Mexico, Inst Tecnol Super Misantla, Artificial Intelligence Lab, Km 1-8 Carretera Loma Cojolite, Veracruz 93821, Mexico.
